Use case label: UC09.01.01
Use Story: US09.01.01
Test case: testPushMakeOnline() in testOffline.java
Participating actor: Owner
Goal : Be able to make inventory items while offline, and push application and expense information online once get connectivity.
Tigger : Borrower's device is currently offline and try to make changes to his inventory
Precondition: Owner clicked into his cached inventory and made some changes to it.
Postcondition: Changes to the inventory are pushed online
Basic Flow:
    Owner makes changes to his inventory
    System pushes the changes to the inventory online as soon as it gets connectivity
